{
  "name": "Web Bind",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Tsuchigumo.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You knead sticky webbing in your mouth and spit it out covering the target area in front of you. <br />Creatures in the target area must succeed a Dexterity saving throw, being restrained on a failed save as the sticky web restricts movement for the duration. <br />A restrained creature makes a Strength saving throw at the end of each of their turns to end this jutsu's effect on them.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the size of the cone by 5 feet.</p>",
